HEADWORD: Flowerless
<hw>Flow"er*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Flowerless plants</b></col>, <cd>plants which have no
